title: Is It Weird To Buy A Push Present For Yourself?
description:
When Cassie had her first kid, her husband gave her a sweet gift in honor of their child. However, he didn't do the same for their second child. This doesn't bother Cassie because she didn't demand that of her husband. But she is considering getting herself a gift in honor of her second child. Is that weird?
